narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Pretty standard Spanish class. Would recommend as a distributional requirement.
Great course, a lot of work but your spanish definitely improves

I would recommend Spanish 140 if a student wants to close up a high school and college career in Spanish and perfect their use of grammar in speech. Keep in mind it is quite a bit of busy work and you have to show up to class every day. There are also a few boring classes from time to time but the material tended to be good I found.
